    <item>
      <title>桑切斯威胁辞职，使西班牙进入选举路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/sanchez-threatens-to-quit-putting-spain-on-course-for-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙法院对其妻子展开调查后，西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯宣布他可能辞职，这将西班牙推向未知的政治领域，并增加了举行新大选的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/sanchez-threatens-to-quit-putting-spain-on-course-for-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其处于“不惜一切代价”模式，但现在不太可能加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-is-in-whatever-it-takes-mode-but-rate-hike-now-unlikely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行可能在不得不考虑再次加息之前赢得了更多时间，一个月前，土耳其央行大幅加息，并实施了进一步的紧缩政策，令市场大吃一惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-is-in-whatever-it-takes-mode-but-rate-hike-now-unlikely</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
